cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a technique for improving the training of deep models, specifically Batch Normalization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Batch Renormalization in computer vision tasks (cs.CV), and the proposed technique involves addressing issues related to non-i.i.d. minibatches (cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper also discusses the benefits of Batch Renormalization in natural language processing tasks (cs.CL).
